{"tid":203250,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"親眼見到佢攬住第個 都唔肯死心","createTime":"2017-04-16T06:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T04:46:58.000Z","uid":103749,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59ffdf024c518f28e8e79030177729252eaddfd1","tid":203250,"uid":103749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:56:00.000Z","msg":"點解可以親眼見到都唔死心<br />\n反而體諒佢<br />\n到底點先可以可以恨恨咁忘記一個人<br />\n時間 幫到 但呢刻好難受<br />\n佢咁快可以同第個一齊<br />\nEasy come easy go<br />\n點解女人可以咁絕情<br />\n男人就拖泥帶水<br />\n我真係唔明白<br />\n我身邊都有人好關心我<br />\n什至肯默默係我身邊 照顧我陪我<br />\n唔介意我仲諗住佢<br />\n但係宜家誰愛我都心領<br />\n覺得自己係零 好垃圾<br />\n咩係雞係公廁 我都不停咁諗佢<br />\n但一訓醒思念就停不了"},{"pid":"a2fc6c5b31a1b4cd05e5ba3b223c004be1f6755c","tid":203250,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:57:58.000Z","msg":"拉殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f6c180fb1c4f2df36e0dd768ff6adc806a1678e","tid":203250,"uid":44423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T06:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>拉殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"885ed4c1199c3f8542bbe416d649c4c9c3368cdb","tid":203250,"uid":103749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:00:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>拉殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係啊 承諾😉😯<br />\n根本就係 一個人人都知既大話<br />\n點解我仲肯咁幼稚去信 去諗<br />\n佢做咩我都可以原諒<br />\n但我只係想佢愛我多一次<br />\n點解都咁難"},{"pid":"1549498c1e30336d1a02a2a3403f3b8321495839","tid":203250,"uid":4150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi